commit message:
Make sure we only get the repository owner and name out of the path, nothing more.

Signed-off-by: Eddie Ringle <eddie@eringle.net>

Fix #27 and close #29 - problems with github url parsing

(uri path starts with a slash, so path[0] is always empty)

In the future could add parsing for github urls like

https://github.com/rtyley/agit/commits/master
https://github.com/rtyley/agit/commit/0b20f717064e68c3115b20615c0cd83be86366ed

To take us to the correct rnch or commit in Agit if the repo already exists...

Use JGit patched for the low-mem deflation loose-object header issue

see:

http://thread.gmane.org/gmane.comp.version-control.git/178752/focus=178923
Add Eddie Ringle to contributor list
